[~rohithsharma]
Thank you for info. Update patch based on below 
# Remove excess attempts only when {{app.attemptFailuresValidityInterval>0}}
# Remove attempts whose finish time is less than {{currenttime-attemptFailuresValidityInterval}}

[~bibinchundatt] Thanks for the patch. 

{quote}
Remove attempts whose finish time is less than currenttime-attemptFailuresValidityInterval.
{quote}
My concern is the number of attempts will be out of control. Suppose in the validity interval, many attempt's exitStatus is ContainerExitStatus.PREEMPTED, ContainerExitStatus.ABORTED, ContainerExitStatus.DISKS_FAILED or ContainerExitStatus.KILLED_BY_RESOURCEMANAGER, they does not count towards max attempt retry, then the attempts's number might be large. Do we need to deal with these cases?
